343
00:27:10,671 --> 00:27:13,966
<i>I think we can do a lot more</i>
<i>than just settle some random scores.</i>

344
00:27:15,050 --> 00:27:16,093
How about this guy?

345
00:27:19,930 --> 00:27:22,766
<i>I don't want people to say</i>
<i>they're scared of it or horrified.</i>

346
00:27:22,850 --> 00:27:24,226
[Mia]<i> What do you want them to say?</i>

347
00:27:25,352 --> 00:27:28,397
[Light]<i> I want them to say... "Thank you."</i>

348
00:27:29,565 --> 00:27:31,358
[laughing]

