354
00:27:46,790 --> 00:27:48,834
[Light]
<i>It's bigger than me. It's bigger than us.</i>

355
00:27:49,501 --> 00:27:50,586
<i>What they want...</i>

356
00:27:51,962 --> 00:27:52,963
<i>is a god.</i>

357
00:27:54,214 --> 00:27:55,340
<i>So let's give it to them.</i>

358
00:27:55,424 --> 00:27:58,427
