361
00:28:04,641 --> 00:28:06,768
[Mia]<i> A god that scares the shit</i>
<i>out of the bad guys</i>

362
00:28:06,852 --> 00:28:08,645
<i>until they don't want to be bad anymore?</i>

363
00:28:08,729 --> 00:28:12,024
[Light]<i> A god who inspires hope</i>
<i>that things can actually change.</i>

364
00:28:13,025 --> 00:28:13,859
Kira.

