387
00:29:22,469 --> 00:29:26,139
<i>This is another bid by the super elites</i>
<i>to sweep the rug from under us</i>

388
00:29:26,223 --> 00:29:28,684
<i>and shape our reality</i>
<i>by what can only be described</i>

389
00:29:28,767 --> 00:29:32,437
