<i>? On the face of the Earth and the sky ?</i>

427
00:32:25,193 --> 00:32:27,654
<i>? Hold onto your breath</i>
<i>Hold onto your heart ?</i>

428
00:32:27,737 --> 00:32:30,115
<i>? Hold onto your hope ?</i>

429
00:32:30,532 --> 00:32:34,327
<i>? Walk up to the gate and let it open ?</i>

430
00:32:47,966 --> 00:32:51,511
