why I didn't bring it up sooner.

434
00:33:00,437 --> 00:33:02,022
What part of terrorists killing each other

435
00:33:02,105 --> 00:33:04,107
and criminals turning themselves in
bothers you, Dad?

436
00:33:04,816 --> 00:33:06,902
